oOD5%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=add79f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=53895003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"755908c98ddd54c6129c6f01921f86d2970e9bc6","tid":1679392,"uid":110503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"4a63e3b3c28b32228f882fb8e6471ec91cde8f21","tid":1679392,"uid":59586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"佢唔係都有份唱榮光咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7BLxdoC8rW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7BLxdoC8rW8&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=a4ee21c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7BLxdoC8rW8</a>"},{"pid":"a400f529d138680f18aacc18887eaca62657f2c1","tid":1679392,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"邊個再upload 就port<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91b13eb87f6d323fbd12a8b4e4f0b7d216981f3","tid":1679392,"uid":37586,"like":1